# Cosmic Collision

### Science Behind the Image

Visualization of a two black holes colliding, and the resulting generated gravitational waves using GR-Chombo simulation for the February 2015 announced event detection by the LIGO experiment.

### Visualization Behind the Image

Created using ParaView with OSPRay.

